|--------|-------|-------|------|-----------|--------------------------|----------|
| Natural — Best Value | 0.49ct | G-VS2 | GIA | ~$680 | ~$1,190 | Smart shoppers avoiding the magic-size premium |
| Natural — Exact Half-Carat | 0.50ct | G-VS2 | GIA | ~$790 | ~$1,300 | Those who need the exact number |
